title: MyKayla Skinner Wins Silver At Tokyo Olympics After Replacing Simone Biles
author: Access
description: Comeback queen! MyKayla Skinner won Silver at the Tokyo Olympics after stepping in for Simone Biles. Her dreams of taking home a medal came true after she crushed the gymnastics vault finals on Sunday. Simone cheered on MyKayla in the stands alongside teammates Jordan Chiles and Grace McCallum and Simone could not have looked happier to see her friend achieve a lifelong goal.
